Careers


At NEXT, we offer our employees the opportunity to grow personally and professionally, to contribute to the success of a dynamic organization, and to serve others in a manner that exceeds their expectations. To ensure our success, NEXT hires results-oriented employees who thrive in a collaborative team environment, and are passionate about providing exceptional customer service. We promote diversity at every level within our organization and believe that employing the very best talent from all groups within the communities in which we live and do business enables us to better serve our customers. If you are someone who wants to help shape the culture of NEXT, then we encourage you to apply today! Benefits at NEXT's Corporate Office & its Subsidiaries NEXT is pleased to provide a comprehensive benefits plan that is responsive to your needs and the needs of your family.  Group Benefits Plan 


