Letter from the President



 

Read More

										
										There is nothing more important to NEXT Financial Group, Inc. (“NEXT”) than helping our Representatives build business their own way.										
					
				






A Bold History



 

Read More

										
										NEXT Financial Group, Inc. ("NEXT") was created when a group of fiercely independent investment representatives grew tired of the repeated mergers and declining service from their broker-dealers.										
					
				






NEXT in the Community



 

Read More

										
										See NEXT's company culture in action as Home Office employees are commited to helping one another through serving the community.										
					
				






Board of Directors



 

Read More

										
										A majority of our board members are NEXT Representatives, shareholders and division managers. Their experience as NEXT advisors dictate their decisions and assist in creating a broker-dealer that is truly rep-focused.										
					
				



 









