NEXT Affiliate Companies
Our affiliate companies are our partners in business, and we would like to extend those partnerships to you. Through our affiliates, NEXT provides added value services such as insurance, third-party money management, acquisitions and succession planning.
NEXT Financial Insurance Service Company
Visit Site
NEXT Financial Insurance Service Company in partnership with Pinnacle (NFISCO) is a full-service national Field Marketing Organization (FMO) dedicated to helping NEXT Representatives and life insurance agents grow their businesses. NFISCO can help position you as a professional with expertise in all aspects of your customers’ financial life cycle. Their team of seasoned professionals is here to provide the support you need to amplify your practice.

Visionary Asset Management
Visit Site
Visionary Asset Management (VAM) offers NEXT’s investment professionals institutional grade money management services. Using innovative management tools and beneficial resources, VAM can help you build business using personalized investment strategies that are fine-tuned to fit your unique financial objectives.





  









